    "info": "ESP32 touch controller PCB — custom board with ESP32-WROOM-32E-N8. OBJECT_TYPE=5 (TOUCH_CONTROLLER), CONTROL_MODE=4 (CONTROL_SINGLE_QUINT). Address and device_id are per-installation; set with HMTLConfig.py --address.",
